Package org.hl7.cdsoutputspecification.r2

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttributeOutputSpecification
    Specifies the attributes contained in the source clinical statement regarding the evaluated person of interest.
    CDSOutputAsDataTypeSpecification
    The parent class specifying the data type output to be provided by a specific CDS use case.
    CDSOutputAsStringNameValuePairSpecification
    The parent class specifying the string name value pair output to be provided by a specific CDS use case.
    CDSOutputAsVMRSpecification
    The parent class specifying the vMR output to be provided by a specific CDS use case.
    CDSOutputSpecification
    Abstract base class specifying the output to be provided by a specific CDS use case.
    ClinicalStatementOutputSpecification
    Specifies the output clinical statements regarding the evaluated person of interest.
    EntityOutputSpecification
    Specifies the entities to be provided as a part of the output.
    EvaluatedPersonOutputSpecification
    Specifies the evaluation results to be provided for an evaluated person.
    ObjectFactory
    This object contains factory methods for each Java content interface and Java element interface generated in the org.hl7.cdsoutputspecification.r2 package.
    PatientOutputSpecification
    The evaluation results to be returned for the patient.
    RelatedClinicalStatementOutputSpecification
    Specifies the clinical statements related to the source clinical statement regarding the evaluated person of interest.
    RelatedEntityOutputSpecification
    Specifies the entities related to the source clinical statement regarding the evaluated person of interest.
    RelatedEvaluatedPersonOutputSpecification
    The results that will be provided for evaluated persons related to the patient.
